def_en: Under- is used to form words that express the idea that there is not enough of something. For example if people are underfed, they are not getting enough food.

def_cn: （置于表示工作或职位的名词前）表示“副…”，“次…”
def_en: Under- is added to the beginning of nouns that refer to a job or rank in order to form nouns that refer to a less important job or rank.
